### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 用户登录
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 创建日记 (需要先登录获取token)
POST http://localhost:3001/diaries
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "今天天气很好，心情也不错！"
}

### 获取日记列表
GET http://localhost:3001/diaries?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 搜索日记
GET http://localhost:3001/diaries/search?keyword=天气&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 获取单篇日记
GET http://localhost:3001/diaries/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 更新日记
PUT http://localhost:3001/diaries/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "更新后的日记内容"
}

### 删除日记
DELETE http://localhost:3001/diaries/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
